Author: thedreamisover
Text: this is so relatable   i used to be obese but lost some weight. sometimes i pick up a box labeled at work as exactly X pounds or smt and my brain is like. “you used to weigh naked as much as you do now holding this heavy ass box + clothes” and then i realize i could lose another box and still be in literally healthy BMI   i guess it’s bc in my mind someone my height could hold two X pounds boxes and be at my HW
